[The change reflects bookkeeping more than epidemiology, with
corrections not to premise numbers but merely to new numbers of
animals affected and further results of laboratory confirmations on
past samples. If there are no new cases in the next week, we may
collectively uncross our fingers, especially if there is a frost or 2
to cut down fly activity. Thanks to Bob, Brent and Joe for the
information. - Mod.MHJ]
